---
title: Beef Meatballs & Peppercorn Sauce with Cheesy Veggie Mash & Tomato Salad
description: A peppery punch with a note of herbs and mushrooms will pop in your mouth when you dig into these plump meatballs.
The sauce will soak into the mashed potatoes and carrot. Add the Parmesan to bring some cheesy goodness to transform the mash and bring everything together into an all time favourite meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

